        <p>While an undergraduate at UCSC, I would tell people that I would run away into the woods after college.
            While I will not be running, hiking a well defined path seemed like a reasonable interpretation of that idea. </p>
        <p>While I have not been backpacking for very long, the dozen trips or so I have embarked on have been wonderful.
            One of my favorite hiking experiences was an 18 mile day hike in 80 degree heat, where we ran out of water...
            I look forward to the challenges the trail will put my mind, body and soul through.</p>
